                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7196" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0495</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9191 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数据管人还是人管数据？数字化工厂工作设计的困境</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Do data govern people or be governed by people? The dilemmas of job design in A digital factory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨晶照，王国栋，朱克颖，葛潇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏索普新材料公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化工厂；工作重塑；自我管理的团队；“阿米巴”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> digital factory; Job remodeling; Self-managed teams; amoeba</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着工厂数字化建设的深入，一切管理以数字为依据，员工逐渐隐身到了数字背后。究竟是人管数据还是数据管人？成为数字化时代下的一个管理困局,组织面临变革。本案例以某大型化工企业DP公司无人化工厂建设过程中的阿米巴实践为切入点，帮助学生理解生产方式数字化转型中，组织结构发生相应变革的必然性与变革方向，理解团队工作的设计与运转对组织结构的有机式转变的作用，促使学生关注工作设计与生产模式的关系。最后，介绍了DP公司的红色阿米巴探索，进一步揭示价值观与文化建设在团队管理中的灵魂作用。通过本案例的学习与思考，分析数字化管理模式下工作设计的难点，通过对DP公司阿米巴实践进程的跟踪与深度剖析，以组织结构变革相关理论为支点，以阿米巴实践表现为自我管理团队为基础分析，更加深入理解组织结构变革与团队建设过程及相关理论，提升管理水平。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the deepening of digital management in factories, all management is based on numbers, and employees are gradually hidden behind numbers. Do data govern people or be governed by people? Become a digital management dilemma. This case is based on the amoeba transformation of SPNM, which is a large chemical enterprise, we analyze the difficulties of team work design in digital factory, and we also introduce the exploration of red amoeba of SPNM company. Then we explain the importance of organization values, and corporate culture in job design. Through in-depth analysis of SPNM amoeba job design process,it can help students understand how to match job design with production and management mode, and promote students to pay attention to the relationship between job design and production mode; At the same time, students are required to apply the theory of job remodeling and motivation theory to find ways to stimulate employees&#39; initiative. Finally, this case will help students examine the problems encountered in job remolding in digital factory, understand the reform process and related theories of job design more deeply, and improve their management level.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理学》、《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织结构变革；工作设计；团队管理；价值观与团队建设</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
